properties.name: Air Combat Command (ACC)
properties.desc:
Joint Base Langley–Eustis, Hampton, Virginia, USA
Air Combat Command (ACC)



Sectors (SOCC) reports to Air Combat Command (ACC) and to NORAD headquarters.
The USAF Air Combat Command portion of the JSS is composed of three Continental United States (CONUS) Sector Operations Control Centers (SOCC) equipped with Battle Control System-Fixed (BCS-F) displays. Three of the SOCCs are located in the Continental United States (CONUS) Source: Wikipedia
